commit.message: Update link to PHP SameSite option in banner
Update ADOdb to 5.22.5 for PHP 8.2+ compatibility
Propagate title changes back to the top-level window, reload orphan pages inside of the frameset (such as when a page is opened in a new tab), plus some code cleanup.
Should be a cleaner fix for https://github.com/ReimuHakurei/phpPgAdmin/pull/7
Remove stuff only needed for PHP versions we don't support, fix some whitespace, and fix the unsupported PostgreSQL message output.
Bugfix: unknown versions should default to latest driver, but this appears to have been broken since PostgreSQL 10.
Bump ADOdb version to fix PHP 8.1 bug.
Fix bytea types not being escaped properly.
